#### PR description: 

This is a test configuration file to create plots similar to the ones in [url](https://indico.cern.ch/event/1015460/contributions/4272289/attachments/2206731/3733812/Akhter_03112021_GEM_CSC_DQM_GUI_lxplus711.pdf)
This code can be checked on DQMOffline code to see if Data vs emulator (comparison) plots can be created.

#### PR validation: 

Tested this code on an lxplus machine using MWGR#2 (2021) data.
